        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Su Jia Nan, once a social outcast, has built a successful writing career, leaving her painful past behind. But when she becomes entangled in a family inheritance dispute, her dreams of becoming a novelist are threatened. With no other options, she turns to Lu Bo Yan, a former high school tormentor now a successful CEO. Desperate to escape their respective family crises, they agree to a marriage contract. But their fake marriage\n\nbrings more complications than solutions, forcing them to confront their pasts and unexpected feelings.",
